 "remarks": "Welcome to 24 Herman Avenue, where classic charm and modern convenience come together in one of Darien&apos;s highly walkable neighborhoods. This sun-filled 4-bedroom, 2-bath Colonial features vaulted ceiling, new flooring, stainless steel appliances, and a beautifully renovated bath with tub and luxurious steam shower. A flexible first-floor bedroom offers the perfect space for a home office, playroom, or guest room. A welcoming front porch and expansive front lawn set the stage for morning coffee, neighborhood gatherings, and endless outdoor play, while the fully fenced backyard creates a private oasis for entertaining, relaxing, or letting family and pets roam freely. Tucked away on a quiet street and just a short stroll to the Noroton Heights train station and Darien&apos;s vibrant new hub for dining, coffee, shopping, and community gathering, this home offers an exceptional blend of charm, convenience, and connection. Move right in and enjoy the small-town feel with abundant amenities that make Darien so desirable.",
